# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ocio Shit — repo root ignore rules
# PRIVACY DECISION (Sprint 1): the personal archive is NEVER committed/published.
# The GitHub repo carries the app SHELL + schema + docs only. The data is loaded
# locally from the user's durable directory.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Personal cultural archive — do NOT publish
data/
*.xlsx
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal

# Durable test folders + durable export files written to disk during manual testing
# (contain the personal archive). Never commit.
carpeta_durable/
**/ocioshit.export.json
**/ocioshit.export.prev.json
**/ocioshit.export.json.tmp

# Design docs + handoff stay LOCAL (contain personal aggregate stats / name / example data).
# The PUBLIC repo carries only the app shell + schema. The app BAKES the tokens.json values
# into its built CSS, so the deployed shell keeps the aesthetic without publishing the source.
# Decision: 2026-06-24.
docs/
diseno/
CLAUDE.md
references/

# Secrets
.env
*.env
!*.env.example

# Node / build artifacts (the app lives in app/)
node_modules/
app/node_modules/
app/.svelte-kit/
app/build/
app/test-results/
app/playwright-report/
app/blob-report/

# Generated by app/scripts/prepare-assets.mjs (recreated on every build) — PUBLIC values only
app/src/lib/db/supabase-config.js

# OS / misc
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
__pycache__/
*.pyc
supabase/.temp/
